</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="120">1.2. Assigning user rights</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Users of the type back end can only access limited sections and menus in the plentymarkets back end. Thus, their access to the system is restricted. If users of this type should be able to work with subscriptions, a user of the type Admin has to assign at least the rights listed in <a href="#table-editing-subscriptions-user-rights-back-end">Table 2</a> to those users.
Subscriptions can be edited with these user rights. In order for users to also create new subscriptions, the rights in <a href="#table-creating-subscriptions-user-rights-back-end">Table 3</a>  have to be assigned <em>additionally</em>.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Assigning user rights for back end users:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
