<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="400">2.2. Creating order items</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>To complete the creation of the subscription, items have to be added. Only then will the subscription be saved and created.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Adding items:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Add</strong> (<span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-plus-square  "></i></span>) in the section <strong>Order items</strong>.<br>
→ You are redirected to the <strong>items</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Add the items in the required quantity to the shopping cart (<span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-cart-plus  "></i></span>). To do this, you can use the item search (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-search  "></i></span>).</p>
</li>
<li>
