<p>Or you can click on <strong>Edit</strong> (<span class="icon yellow-background"><i class="fa fa-pencil  "></i></span>) and be redirected directly to the shopping cart (<span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-cart-plus  "></i></span>) of the subscription. The following editing options are available to you there:</p>
