<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="1200">4.1. Searching for subscriptions</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Use filters to search (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-search  "></i></span>) for subscriptions in the subscription overview.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Proceed as follows to search for subscriptions:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
