<p>Go to the <strong>Orders » subscription</strong> menu.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter search terms in the search fields or set filter options. Pay attention to the explanations given in <a href="#table-search-subscriptions">Table 6</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Search</strong> (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-search  "></i></span>).<br>
→ The subscriptions that match the search criteria are listed.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
